# .env.example
# AT Medical .github organization repository
#
# This repository is a governance and configuration repository with no runtime application.
# No environment variables are required for normal operation.
#
# If you add tooling that requires environment configuration, document the required
# variables here. Never commit real values — use only placeholder notation.

# Example (do not use real values):
# GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here
# GITLEAKS_LICENSE=your_gitleaks_license_here
